      "rationale": "NIH is the primary regulatory metric for hemolysis assessment in CPB devices per FDA guidance. Wall shear stress is the mechanistic driver of red blood cell damage in the power-law hemolysis model. Both QoIs directly inform the worst-case operating condition identification required by the COU."
