      "acceptanceCriteria": "The turbulence model and hemolysis damage model must be justified for the flow regime and validated against relevant experimental data.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on documented performance for rotating machinery flows at the Reynolds numbers encountered (Re ~ 10^4–10^5). Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) employed with published coefficients. Model form justified by literature review and confirmed by validation comparison. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
